    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lift your eyes up and look from where you are."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When you see the Christ, our all-inclusive land,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then we walk in this blessed land, enjoying all we see,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Getting saved eating milk and honey."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "See the wheat, the restricted Jesus Christ."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Incarnation was restriction in the flesh."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Limited outwardly, by God’s power set free,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Resurrected as unlimited barley."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "See the vine trees, the sacrificing Christ."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He produced wine thus cheering God and man."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When we drink this new wine, we are so energized,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For the Lord to be a living sacrifice."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "See the fig trees, Christ’s sweetness our supply."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To progress in the joy of all our faith,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Be a channel of supply so others experience Christ,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And be happy in the bountiful supply."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "See the pomegranates, fulness of His life;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The abundance and the beauty of this life."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As the olive tree the Spirit fills to honor God and man,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Bearing fruit as branches grafted into Christ."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "See our portion so available to take,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To be walked in and experienced in full."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Apprehending the unsearchable extent of this good land,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When we corporately enjoy Him with the saints."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "7"
    }
